{
  "texts": [
    "In this area, we can also see a product such as PySyft-TensorFlow (PySyftTF 2023), which is a collaboration effort between the Syft community and the TensorFlow community.",
    "The framework brings secure, private DL to TensorFlow.",
    "However, it will soon be deprecated in favor of PySyft.",
    "This fusion-shattering example shows the dynamical evolving state in this applied research area.",
    "Flower (Flower 2023) is a Python library that provides a unified approach to FL, analytics, and evaluation with its motto: An unified approach to federated learning, analytics, and evaluation."
  ]
}